Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.40,0:17:43.76,Default CN,,0,0,0,,來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.82,0:17:46.47,Default JP,,0,0,0,,気をつけて！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.82,0:17:46.47,Default CN,,0,0,0,,小心！
